{"tid":1642734,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下全民感謝日你地食左咩","createTime":"2019-10-10T00:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T03:43:09.000Z","uid":296789,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4a506f0061a8fa6f9356edaeb60f3a5ccc4c61","tid":1642734,"uid":296789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:10:05.000Z","msg":"我先！<br />\n尋晚已經開左波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一間係堅尼地城既beeger<br />\n氣氛幾chill<br />\n入去果時係full house咖<br />\n但我食到好夜 所以影到好似冇哂人咁<br />\n如果室外座位望海好好feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgcG2KM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgcG2KM.jpg&h=5ccdba43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TSyfnKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTSyfnKc.jpg&h=135642be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BBFtHKw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBBFtHKw.jpg&h=ce22d202&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yo9x9p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYo9x9p4.jpg&h=5dc307ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個burger睇落普通 但一切就已經爆汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三文魚好濃味 我竟然可以一條友食哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n單骨蜜糖雞翼脆脆地幾好食 食埋就好飽啦~<br />\n佢鋪頭入面都有少量文宣咖<br />\n<br />\n得閒再share埋其他食過既黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我p牌仔推唔郁 咁多位ching請出手寫食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">飲飲食食 不遺餘力</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f8e969c42cf5f8ce81c887a15f3e8c094a79f572","tid":1642734,"uid":8486,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T00:56:02.000Z","msg":"灣仔 文華饕記<br />\n616已經開始支持<br />\n